desc.en: The London Underground is an urban rail transit system in London,UK.It is the first subway in the world and was completed and opened to traffic on Januaryn10,1863.Subway vehicles run nderground in central London, and run on the ground to the suburbs,of which 55% of ground running lines.London has built a 408-kilometre-long subway network,of which 160 kilometres are underground,with a total of 12 lines and 275 operating stations.（This Map is copied by one person,and there may be flaws！）
